{"tid":1464663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"見到大家互屌最開心咪班三毛同狗","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:18:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:57:50.000Z","uid":33205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"69105effce11f7929212e18b900a053e37f4feaf","tid":1464663,"uid":33205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:18:16.000Z","msg":"記住 各有各做 事後先檢討 唔好一黎就屌晒鬼 大家都係共同目標既戰友<br />\n唔好俾分化撚有機可乘<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不篤灰、不指責、不分化、不割蓆</span></span>"},{"pid":"6b7bef3ca4efd68883c902dd8cd93da836baa5e1","tid":1464663,"uid":6363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:18:35.000Z","msg":"大家聽住。<br />\n知唔知點解政府811咁撚豬會畀你地影到示威者入面有鬼？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而唔繼續鬼落去<br />\n<br />\n其實佢地呢招好撚高，政府知我地核彈都唔撚割。所以特登話你知：我地放咗鬼喺你度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等你次次都疑神疑鬼，等戰友間失去咗互相信任。<br />\n<br />\n大家諗吓，由612 走到而家，我地本住一句核彈都唔割先得。所以，所有檢討post，要等該日完咗先好出。仲有唔好懷疑自己身邊嘅人，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">戰友總畀警鬼多</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆、不譴責、不篤灰、不分化、不足鬼<br />\n</span></strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"66bda0c5783af72cfb2058ef1de5275c96ec9041","tid":1464663,"uid":33205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:19:05.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"07ee47ca112e507f608eab6fca0697522936099d","tid":1464663,"uid":60321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:19:19.000Z","msg":"大家依家要預左個個星期都係咁比人分化架喇<br />\n只係每當大家以為個運動會分化到散 <br />\n到星期六日大家都係如常走返哂出黎 又滿返士氣<br />\n<br />\n總之唔好輕敵 的確係難打<br />\n同埋有時人多 有人犯錯有人鬧交好難避免 <br />\n唔係樣樣野都到自己控制 但你可以決定繼續出黎<br />\n總之鬧完交就繼續出黎 繼續做自己認為啱既事<br />\n記住不斷提醒大家係一team人 不分化<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好灰心 大家繼續加油"},{"pid":"8a2ea1f61bd182154a15bcb30a60b23555887fda","tid":1464663,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:20:03.000Z","msg":"［正視聽］大家唔好再嘈啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464495\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464495</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8ec03c98115c25762ebee2205750921b1981e909","tid":1464663,"uid":33205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:21:05.000Z","msg":"前線都可以有鬼 連登冇人攪事講你都唔信啦<br />\n唔好俾佢地有機可乘就得"},{"pid":"fd69f971b6194c91580b5bf9699d392e84095db8","tid":1464663,"uid":33205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:22:51.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"ed44cb94587acc3cae5cbd30711b9e720baa6d09","tid":1464663,"uid":33205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:24:03.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"3fa34cb7f8b1358db016b38be45d1420de2b4c57","tid":1464663,"uid":33205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:57:50.000Z","msg":"7"}]}